The '''Renatasian Confederation''' was a loose association of [[Human/Legends|human]] exiles from the destroyed nation-states of the [[Renatasia system/Legends|Renatasia system]]. Led by [[Klyn Shanga]], these fighter aces sought to hunt down the [[Butcher of Renatasia]]. They eventually killed [[Osuno Whett/Legends|Osuno Whett]], the man responsible for betraying Renatasia to the [[Centrality/Legends|Centrality]] and the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]].

The group included [[Bern Nuladeg]], and [[Colonel/Legends|Colonel]] [[Kenow]], veteran [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] and close friends of Shanga, who came out of retirement to help in the quest for vengeance.

